import Form from './styles/Form';

export default function  SignIn(){
    //method POST also does't let the url have the input after submit of the input
    return <Form> 
        <fieldset>
        <label htmlFor="email">Email</label>
        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Your Email Addrress" autoComplete="email"></input>
        <label htmlFor="password">Email</label>
        <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="Password" autoComplete="password"></input>
        <label htmlFor="email">Email</label>
        <input type="email" name="email"></input>
        </fieldset>
    </Form>
    }
